	Teamswap					- sm_teamswap / sm_swapteam - <player1> <player2> etc etc. Or no args to swap entire team
	Move player team			- sm_team <player/@ALL/@CT/@T> <teamid>  (CSS 1-spec, 2-t, 3-ct)
